verbose_text: To determine whether TK was secreted by proliferating T cells, T cells were co-cultured for 48 hours with gamma irradiated OKT3 loaded CLN4 and cytokines which resulted in elevated TK levels (28.6 +/- 2.5 U/L) in the conditioned supernatant compared to gamma irradiated T cells (p = 0.03) and T cells co-cultured with cytokines only (p = 0.04) (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY).
